<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Simlei Nunnawp Chawmcha</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Simlei nunnawp chawmcha bawn I thaklah chun,
 Nunnawp tawplo van nawpna chu hawl hitiu;
 $ Simlei maunan a dim hi,
 Ken vang kipahna ka mu puoi; D.S
 Nunnawp tawplo van nawpna chu hawl hitiu.

[V2]
 2. Hinna gimum chawmcha hi bawn I ngaih chun,
 Kipah nawpna van hinna hi zawm hitiu,
 $ Migilote chan ding chu,
 Bible-in gawtmun a gen hi D.S
 Kipah nawpna van hinna hi zawm hitiu.

[V3]
 3. Utleh, utloh thu him him chu dawng lo-in,
 Nicheng thihnan sang tamtak a puimang zing,
 $ Thih muon theihna I ngai ui,
 Lei a umden ding I um puou D.S.
 Thihna zopa Lal Krista hi bel hitiu.

[V4]
 4. Puipa I ngai zie khawvel gimum ahin,
 Puipa I ngai khawvel I pawtsan nin le;
 $ Thihna dak a hung tunga,
 Van Ina ei tunsak dingin D.S.
 Puipa I ngai Lal Krista Thagau ngei chu.</lyrics>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>211</hymn_number>
</song>